  <description><![CDATA[<p>Two of Italy's most famous lakes are situated within in easy reach of each other and this twin centre holiday with included excursions gives you the opportunity to explore both lakes in one go.</p>
<p>During your 4 night stay in Lake Maggiore you will be staying in the main town of <a data-udi="umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b}" title="Stresa">Stresa</a> where you might like to explore the nearby Borromean Islands or botanical gardens. Then transfer to Lake Como with its famous villas where you will be based in the delightful resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/8b37cb2bfc354628b321751c199d4032" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8b37cb2bfc354628b321751c199d4032}" title="Cadenabbia">Cadenabbia</a> for 7 nights. During your stay you will enjoy an included full day excursion to St Moritz which features a ride on the world famous Bernina Express train as well as a half day excursion to the historic, medieval city of Bergamo. In both resorts, the Inghams Representatives will be on hand to advise and assist and help you enjoy your holiday to the full.</p>
<p> </p>
